40:41.774 --> 40:43.614
WOODROW: The river's back that way.

40:43.776 --> 40:45.436
We've been going in circles.

40:48.280 --> 40:50.280
ABNER: I've never
been out this far before.

41:19.019 --> 41:20.689
WOODROW: Do you
know where we are?

41:24.733 --> 41:26.363
BOBBY: Look at this. (LAUGHS)

41:26.902 --> 41:28.322
WOODROW: What on Earth?

41:29.655 --> 41:30.985
ABNER: You've got to see this.

41:45.087 --> 41:46.417
You think that kid did all this?

41:47.173 --> 41:49.093
What would a kid be doing this far out?

41:50.718 --> 41:51.958
GAVIN: Hey, guys! Look at this.

41:53.345 --> 41:54.345
(GROWLS)

41:56.056 --> 41:57.216
Run!

42:03.564 --> 42:04.574
(SHOUTING)

42:05.691 --> 42:06.781
GAVIN: Hurry up!

42:06.859 --> 42:08.739
