42:30.966 --> 42:31.966
Come on, let's go!

42:32.968 --> 42:34.258
Go, go, go!

42:34.386 --> 42:35.386
(GROANS)

42:35.554 --> 42:36.764
BOBBY: What is that?

42:40.726 --> 42:42.436
Drive, man! Go!

42:43.103 --> 42:44.103
(GROANS)

42:48.984 --> 42:49.994
(GRUNTS)

42:54.073 --> 42:55.123
(SHOUTING)

43:27.189 --> 43:28.189
(SNEEZES)

43:32.152 --> 43:33.612
Gavin, come on!

43:33.696 --> 43:34.776
(ALL SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)

43:42.329 --> 43:43.409
WOODROW: What was that?

43:43.497 --> 43:44.497
BOBBY: What was that?

