GAVIN: Did you see that?

43:48.502 --> 43:49.502
Did you see that?

43:49.670 --> 43:51.273
- It was a monster!
- No, man, that was a demon.

43:51.297 --> 43:52.337
It was a monster demon.

43:52.506 --> 43:53.876
It was a dragon!

44:03.976 --> 44:05.886
You put the needle on, and...

