44:14.695 --> 44:16.275
<i>Yes, it's a good day</i>

44:16.363 --> 44:18.123
(MUSIC DISTORTS)

44:18.198 --> 44:20.158
<i>For singing this song</i>

44:20.242 --> 44:21.242
<i>And it's a good day</i>

44:21.368 --> 44:22.368
(MUSIC RETURNS TO NORMAL)

44:22.494 --> 44:23.544
Let it play.

44:23.620 --> 44:24.750
<i>For moving along</i>

44:24.830 --> 44:27.670
<i>Yes it's a good day
How could anything go wrong?</i>

44:27.750 --> 44:29.500
That's me, and that's my dad.

44:30.711 --> 44:31.881
That's his brother.

44:32.004 --> 44:34.724
There's Grace. That's my family.

44:35.382 --> 44:36.382
Family.

44:38.552 --> 44:40.012
That's what we are.

44:40.387 --> 44:41.387
(MUSIC CONTINUES)

44:41.472 --> 44:43.812
<i>Everything to gain and nothing to lose</i>

44:43.891 --> 44:45.141
Mmm...

44:45.225 --> 44:47.475
<i>A good day from morning till night</i>

44:47.561 --> 44:51.191
NATALIE: Put your head here,
scooch down...

44:51.357 --> 44:54.397
and now you're five years old.

44:55.402 --> 44:59.032
<i>You know you got to get going
